node.text:
We reached 400K! We would like to say a big thank you to all of our supporters! We will continue to spread the news about the Starship Program! 💫

To celebrate us reaching an amazing milestone of 400K followers! We are releasing our new HLS program poster, shirt and hoodies! SpaceX has been through a turbulent situation with NASA. You can now show your support towards your favourite HLS lander design. 

To say thank you, use HLS400K for 30% off all our designs. Link in the bio!

Credit to @tomdixondesign and @austin8barnard  for designing us these amazing posters!
.
